summary: DONALD DUCK - In a world where business tycoons and cartoon icons collide, one figure stands out. Imagine the fiery temper of Donald Duck combined with the bombastic personality of Donald Trump. Feathers fly and quacks resound as this larger-than-life character waddles into the political spotlight, shaking up conventions with every webbed footstep. Brace yourself for a presidential run like no other, where tantrums are tweets and deals are "yuge"! Welcome to the quacktastic realm of Donald Duck Trump!
